item.description: Have a question or just want to say hi? Send us an email at contact@nanr.io or fill out the form below Email Message Send Thank you for getting in touch. We'll get back to you shortly.

What is a Nanr? A Nanr is a digital token that can be purchased for abour $0.25 and later sold back to nanr Why would I want to buy Nanrs? A Nanr's can be given to anyone for any reason. Read a great blog post? Given them a Nanr. Watch a great video? Give em a Nanr! Why would I want to buy Nanrs? A Nanr's can be given to anyone for any reason.

Integrate Your Blog or Website With Nanr With just one line of html you can add a Nanr button anywhere on the page. Just one click transfers a Nanr from the person clicking the button to you. Nanr's can be exchanged for cash - $0.18 per Nanr. Did we mention that putting a Nanr button on your page is 100% free? You can make the button as small as 40x40.
